<br>
I use Linux for various tasks from development, through Internet usage to gaming and I must admit it is far more stable than a lot of other OS's. You can also get win32 emulators (Linux pretending to be Windows) which allow you to run some applications. You can now get Internet Explorer for Linux and I believe that many other apps will follow.<br>
